These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, cola, milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, soccer
1. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person drinking water is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | water | cola | milk   |
| Sport      | cricket    | cycling  | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, water, coffee
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, mexican, chinese
1. the polish is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the mexican is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | water | juice     | coffee      |
| Nationality   | mexican | polish | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, papaya, grapefruit
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea  | coffee       |
| Food       | cucumber     | papaya | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, eggplant, cauliflower
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, chess, fishing
1. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | cauliflower    | eggplant     | peas |
| Hobby   | fishing | photography | chess     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, chinchilla
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
4. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | hamster | cat     | chinchilla |
| Transport   | boat        | tram | snowmobile    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, lime, potato
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, helicopter
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person eating lime is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person eating potato is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | potato | cucumber      | lime  |
| Transport   | roller       | jet-ski | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, techno, d&b
3 different pets are kept: frog, pony, turtle
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of techno is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | electronic     | techno    |
| Pet           | frog | turtle | pony |

 #################################

 
