.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, juice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, documentary
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | fanta    | juice    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | crime | documentary |

