The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, hip-hop, indie
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | coffee  | mirinda | soy-milk  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | indie   | metal |

