The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, indie
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | dancing | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | indie     | r&b  |

