.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, nectarine, lettuce
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, sailing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | lettuce | garlic       | nectarine  |
| Sport   | biathlon  | sailing | water-polo |

 